# 11. Use Case Design Principles

## Intent First

Users describe goals, not technical instructions.

---

## Execution Focused

AI performs actions, not only provides answers.

---

## Human Controlled

Important actions require approval.

---

## Extensible

Developers can add new capabilities.

---

## Scalable

Use cases can expand from individuals to enterprises.

---

